## Phase 0 — Design tokens groundwork

**Goal:** later phases must not hardcode values, so tokens come first.
**Why:** rules say "Use ThemeExtensions" and "No magic numbers", but
`core/theme/app_theme.dart` currently has no spacing/radius/semantic-color tokens.

Tasks:
- [ ] Add `AppSpacing` (xs/sm/md/lg/xl) and `AppRadius` (chip/card/sheet) constants in `core/theme/`.
- [ ] Add a `ThemeExtension` for semantic colors: success (green), warning (amber), danger (red), surface tints for chips/fills — pulled from the values already used in screens.
- [ ] Add text-style tokens for the two recurring micro-styles: amber caps eyebrow, gray caps section header (min 11sp, reduced letter-spacing).
- [ ] No screen changes in this phase beyond compiling.

Files: `lib/core/theme/app_theme.dart` (+ new `spacing.dart` if cleaner).
Accept when: tokens exist, `flutter analyze` clean, zero visual diff.

