## Phase 1 — Text integrity (highest leverage — kills the loudest "unfinished" tells)

**Why:** "1 sessions attended" appears on every roster row and player card;
Register ships truncated placeholders ("Height (Optio…"). These are the fastest
signals of low quality in the whole app.

Tasks:
- [ ] Convert `sessionsAttended` in `lib/l10n/app_en.arb` + `app_ar.arb` from a bare suffix string to an ICU plural taking `count` (`{count, plural, one{1 session attended} other{{count} sessions attended}}`; Arabic gets full zero/one/two/few/many/other forms). Update all call sites; run `flutter gen-l10n`.
- [ ] Same treatment for "spots left", waitlist counts, and any other `"$n $suffix"` concatenations (grep for string interpolation next to l10n getters).
- [ ] Fix truncation: player-card subtitle ("1 sessions at…") — shorten the string or give the name/subtitle column priority over the trailing chip; roster names get 2-line wrap or tighter trailing icons.
- [ ] Copy fixes: announcement composer button "Save" → "Post"; "Sessions History" → "Session History"; title-case location names at render time (util in `core/utils/`).
- [ ] Register screen: stop relying on placeholders for "Height (Optional)" / "Weight (Optional)" — interim fix here, full field system in Phase 2.

Files: `lib/l10n/app_en.arb`, `app_ar.arb`, regenerated `app_localizations*.dart`,
`core/widgets/session_card.dart`, `features/players/presentation/screens/players_tab.dart`,
session detail screens, `features/auth/presentation/screens/register_screen.dart`,
announcements screens, `features/sessions/.../recurring_sessions_screen.dart` (history title).
Accept when: no English/Arabic string ever renders a wrong plural; nothing truncates
on a 360dp-wide device; both locales checked.

