## Phase 8 — Coaches screen alignment

Source: `app-ui-screenshots/coaches-screen.png` (added 2026-07-12 — missed the original audit).

**Why:** the Coaches screen never got the premium pass and is now the last list
screen on the old visual language. Each row is an oversized bare pill — 72dp
avatar, name, kebab, and nothing else — with a hand-rolled initials avatar
whose gold-at-20%-over-navy disc renders muddy grey-brown. The initials logic
is duplicated (it already lives in `RingedAvatar` and `PlayerCard`'s avatar),
and the kebab menu's ONLY item is destructive account deletion, exposed on
every row a coach can see. Note: `CoachSummary` carries only uid/name/photoUrl
— no attendance data — so coach rows must not assume tier art.

Tasks:
- [ ] One avatar fallback app-wide: extract the initials-avatar (photo → gold-on-navy initials) into a shared `core/widgets/` component and use it from `RingedAvatar`, `PlayerCard`, and the coach card — refactor the shared widgets, don't fork a fourth copy. Kills the muddy disc.
- [ ] Rebuild the coach row on the `PlayerCard` silhouette (same padding, radius, border, shadow, name-first hierarchy) — either reuse `PlayerCard` with its tier/attendance elements optional, or a sibling card built from the same extracted pieces. No 72dp-avatar empty pill.
- [ ] Give the card content beside the bare name: "COACH" role eyebrow (Phase 0 `AppTextStyles.eyebrow`) as the quiet meta line; count eyebrow above the list ("3 COACHES") to match the Players header discipline. New strings → EN+AR `.arb` + `gen-l10n`.
- [ ] Destructive hygiene (Phase 5/7 rule): a menu must not contain ONLY a destructive item. Add "View profile" (→ existing viewer-aware `player_profile_screen.dart`) as the first menu item and/or make the row tappable to the profile; "Delete account" stays last, red, behind `confirm_dialog.dart` (already is). Player viewers see no kebab at all (already true — keep it).
- [ ] Tokens: spacing/radius from `AppSpacing`/`AppRadius`, semantic colors from the Phase 0 extension; RTL + 360dp checked.

Files: `features/coaches/presentation/screens/coaches_tab.dart`,
`features/players/presentation/widgets/player_card.dart` (generalize),
`core/widgets/ringed_avatar.dart`, new shared avatar widget in `core/widgets/`,
`lib/l10n/app_en.arb` + `app_ar.arb`.
Accept when: the coaches list speaks the same visual language as the Players list
(card silhouette, avatar treatment, header discipline); initials logic exists exactly
once; no row exposes a destructive-only menu; both locales + RTL pass.

